        <h2 id="ui-fails-grumpy-website">UI fails: Grumpy Website</h2>
<p>Über einen Artikel über <a href="https://grumpy.website/post/0S6F8ozn5">schlimmes Dashboard Design im Renault</a> stieß ich auf die [Grumpy Website(<a href="https://grumpy.website">https://grumpy.website</a>), wo jede Menge kleine und große UI fails gesammelt werden.</p>
<blockquote>
<p>My favorite theory (which is yet to be challenged) is that modern car interfaces are designed by people who have never even seen a car in their entire life.</p>
</blockquote>


